        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Oregon Hill is suffering from food insecurity due to limited access to affordable, healthy food...</p>
        <p><strong>Key Issues:</strong> Limited Grocery Stores, Impact of Gentrification, Health Concerns...</p>
