        <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Oregon Hill faces multiple environmental risks, including lead paint exposure, air pollution, and urban heat...</p>
        <p><strong>Key Issues:</strong> Lead Paint, Air Quality, Urban Heat Island Effect...</p>
        <img src="environmental-issues.jpg" alt="Environmental Hazards" />
