    <section id="conclusion">
        <h2>Conclusion and Recommendations</h2>
        <p>Oregon Hill faces numerous challenges, but the community’s resilience offers hope for overcoming these obstacles...</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Lead paint abatement programs</li>
            <li>Improved air quality monitoring</li>
            <li>Expansion of green spaces</li>
        </ul>
